tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE energy_prices (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    price DECIMAL,
    provider VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE energy_consumption (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    consumption DECIMAL,
    location VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE market_demand (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    demand DECIMAL,
    region VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    data DECIMAL,
    source VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE market_strategies (
    strategy_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    strategy_name VARCHAR,
    description TEXT
)
